Answer: block:
- name: Ensure API key is provided
  ansible.builtin.fail:
    msg: api_key needs to be defined in tests/integration/integration_config.yml
  when:
  - api_key is not defined
  - api_key | length == 0
- name: Create Cron job to deploy new container template
  community.healthchecksio.checks:
    state: present
    channels: '*'
    api_key: ''
    name: container_template_deployment
    unique:
    - name
    schedule: 7 7 * * *
    tz: UTC
    template:
    - name: docker-compose
      image: wrouesnel/docker-compose:latest
      command: -f /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks/docker-compose.yml
      environment:
        ACME_EMAIL: ''
        ACME_KEY: ''
        API_KEY: ''
        CONTAINER_TEMPLATE_NAME: ''
        DATA_SOURCE_NAME: db
        DISCOVERY_IMAGE: wrouesnel/discovery:latest
        DISCOVERY_NAME: discovery
        DISCOVERY_PORT: '50051'
        ENABLE_DISCOVERY: 'true'
        MEMCACHED_HOST: localhost
        NGINX_IMAGE: nginx:latest
        NGINX_PORT: '80'
        POLLERS: '6'
        POLLERS_CRON: '7 7 * * *'
        POLLERS_DISCOVERY_ENABLE: 'true'
        POLLERS_DISCOVERY_INTERVAL: '6'
        POLLERS_DISCOVERY_WAIT: '3'
        SERVICE_NAME: mailcow
    wait_for_status:
      status: started
    timeout: '600'
- name: Check status of the Cron job
  ansible.builtin.command: /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks/docker-compose status
    -f /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks/docker-compose.yml
  args:
    chdir: /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks
- name: Copy the docker-compose.yml template into the installation directory
  ansible.builtin.template:
    src: docker-compose.yml.j2
    dest: /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks/docker-compose.yml
    owner: root
    group: root
    mode: 420
- name: Run the docker-compose.yml file to install the healthchecks app
  ansible.builtin.command: /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks/docker-compose up
    -f /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks/docker-compose.yml
  args:
    chdir: /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks
- name: Enable healthchecks docker-compose service
  ansible.builtin.systemd:
    name: mailcow-docker-healthchecks
    enabled: true
- name: Remove the healthchecks docker-compose file
  ansible.builtin.file:
    path: /opt/mailcow-docker-healthchecks/docker-compose.yml
    state: absent

when: not tmux_version_installed.stdout is search(tmux_version)
block:
- name: Gathering facts
  ansible.builtin.setup:
    gather_subset: min
- name: Installing Ubuntu/Debian dependencies
  ansible.builtin.apt:
    name:
    - automake
    - bison
    - gcc
    - git
    - libevent-dev
    - libncurses5-dev
    - make
    - pkg-config
    state: present
  when: ansible_pkg_mgr == 'apt'
- name: Installing Fedora/EL dependencies
  ansible.builtin.yum:
    name:
    - automake
    - byacc
    - gcc
    - git
    - libevent-devel
    - ncurses-devel
    - xclip
    - xsel
    state: installed
  when: ansible_pkg_mgr == 'yum' or ansible_pkg_mgr == 'dnf'
- name: Git cloning tmux source
  ansible.builtin.git:
    repo: https://github.com/tmux/tmux.git
    dest: /usr/src/tmux
    version: 3.3a
- name: Running autogen.sh
  ansible.builtin.command: /bin/sh autogen.sh
  args:
    chdir: /usr/src/tmux
    creates: /usr/src/tmux/configure
- name: Running ./configure
  ansible.builtin.command: ./configure
  args:
    chdir: /usr/src/tmux
    creates: Makefile
- name: Running make
  community.general.make:
    chdir: /usr/src/tmux
    params:
      NUMTHREADS: 4
- name: Installing via make install
  community.general.make:
    chdir: /usr/src/tmux
    target: install
- name: Adding /usr/local/bin to PATH via /etc/profile.d/tmux.sh
  ansible.builtin.copy:
    src: tmux.sh
    dest: /etc/profile.d/tmux.sh
    mode: '0644'
  when: ansible_os_family == 'RedHat'

yum:
  name: http://repo.zabbix.com/zabbix/4.0/rhel/6/x86_64/zabbix-release-4.0-1.el6.noarch.rpm
  state: present
starcoder-response:
name: Install zabbix repo

Answer: when:
- ansible_distribution in [ "CentOS", "RedHat", "Rocky" ] or ansible_os_family in
  [ "Debian", "Suse" ]
block:
- name: Manage crypto policy
  when:
  - ansible_os_family == "RedHat"
  - ansible_distribution_major_version == "9"
  block:
  - name: Install crypto-policies-scripts
    ansible.builtin.package:
      name: crypto-policies-scripts
    notify:
    - Uninstall crypto-policies-scripts
  - name: Get current crypto policy
    ansible.builtin.command:
      cmd: update-crypto-policies --show
    changed_when: false
    register: elastic_repo_current_crypto_policy
  - name: Switch to legacy crypto policy
    ansible.builtin.command:
      cmd: update-crypto-policies --set LEGACY
    changed_when: true
    when:
    - elastic_repo_current_crypto_policy.stdout!= "LEGACY"
    notify:
    - Switch back to default crypto policy
- name: Install rpm key
  ansible.builtin.rpm_key:
    key: '{{ _zabbix_rpm_key[ansible_os_family][ansible_distribution_major_version]
      | default(_zabbix_rpm_key[''default'']) }}'
    state: present
  when:
  - ansible_pkg_mgr in [ "dnf", "yum", "zypper" ]
- name: Install (dnf/yum)
  ansible.builtin.package:
    name: '{{ _zabbix_repository_package[ansible_distribution] | default(_zabbix_repository_package[ansible_os_family])
      }}'
    state: present
  register: zabbix_repository_install_dnf_yum
  when:
  - ansible_pkg_mgr in [ "dnf", "yum" ]
- name: Install (apt)
  ansible.builtin.apt:
    deb: '{{ _zabbix_repository_package[ansible_distribution] | default(_zabbix_repository_package[ansible_os_family])
      }}'
  register: zabbix_repository_install_apt
  when:
  - ansible_pkg_mgr == "apt"
  notify:
  - Update cache
- name: Install (zypper}
  community.general.zypper:
    name: '{{ _zabbix_repository_package[ansible_distribution] | default(_zabbix_repository_package[ansible_os_family])
      }}'
    state: present
    disable_gpg_check: true
  register: zabbix_repository_install_zypper
  when:
  - ansible_pkg_mgr == "zypper"
- name: Fail when yum/dnf, apt and zypper are skipped
  ansible.builtin.fail:
    msg: This system does not support yum, dnf or apt.
  when:
  - zabbix_repository_install_dnf_yum is skipped
  - zabbix_repository_install_apt is skipped
  - zabbix_repository_install_zypper is skipped
- name: Create /etc/zabbix
  ansible.builtin.file:
    path: /etc/zabbix
    state: directory
    mode: '0755'
- name: Enable zabbix-frontend
  community.general.ini_file:
    path: /etc/yum.repos.d/zabbix.repo
    section: zabbix-frontend
    option: enabled
    value: '1'
    mode: '0644'
  when:
  - ansible_os_family in [ "RedHat", "Rocky" ]
  - ansible_distribution_major_version == "7"
